org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT users.* FROM users INNER JOIN members ON members.user_id = users.id WHERE users.status = "$1" AND members.project_id = 1 AND users.status = "$2" AND users.status = "$3" AND users.type IN ("$4", "$5") ORDER BY users.type DESC, users.firstname, users.lastname, users.id
